reviewText: 4-out continuity but nothing else really 'Princeton' about it.  Might work well for junior high or high school JV.  Personally I am staying away from anything Angelli does ad he apparently likes to use flavor of the week buzz words to deceive buyers and increase sales.

The advertisement and the video state it has pdf embedded in the DVD as support material to teach with. My copy does not include this, I did call as the coach said he was readily available to answer any questions...and got no response.
Shipped quickly and met my expectations.  Very well done and easy to understand breakdown of offense.  We will be using this offense next season.
Breaks this offense down. Makes it very easy to learn and love how it goes into transition portion as well. Product shipped early as well
